~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : demote                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : demote <username> 

   This will demote a user to the next level down from the one he is 
   currently at.  You can only demote a user of a lower level than 
   yourself.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : promote, pop
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
